<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />The Ephraimites were armed with bows,</para>

<para style="q1">but they turned back on the day of battle.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />They did not keep the covenant with God,</para>

<para style="q1">and they refused to obey his law.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />They forgot his deeds,</para>

<para style="q1">the wonderful things that he had shown them.</para>
